{"tid":1561327,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］點對付休班警有警棍？","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T00:07:15.000Z","uid":306647,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6652187e721f20232dff26cb06bd0964662f19bd","tid":1561327,"uid":306647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此乃香城Online攻略</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">純學術討論</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n休班警獲發警棍簡本係警權<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無限延伸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n休班警係用警棍之前肯定會call定軍裝，所以如果我地要郁手，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要係軍裝到之前</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以預期一樣野，小小亂都好，休班狗都會淆，會拎定枝警棍係手，到時佢四面都係人，佢亦根本分辨唔到邊個係市民，邊個係示威者，所以好可能會亂咁揮動警棍，或者見到有黑衫就會打，反正依家打人無成本<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅情況，<br />\n<br />\n簡單講得一個目標，就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒收佢枝警棍</span></span>，拎到手就即刻收起，然後Be Water，全部散水，因為每枝休班警用嘅警棍都會有特別標記（可能會有埋編號），即係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢嘅身份會同枝警棍綁埋一齊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沒收警棍有三個好處：<br />\n<br />\n第一，避免之後發夢個陣，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">休班狗便裝突然出手</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">，手足被捉到嘅可能性會大增</span></span>，要保護前線，尼啲便裝休班狗嘅警棍，一定要沒收<br />\n<br />\n第二，如果隻休班狗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">亂鳩咁打人</span></span>，沒收警棍有佢嘅必要，正如你見到有人用武器打人都會出手制止，沒收返尼嘅警棍之後可以係民事索償時，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">作呈堂證供</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第三，警棍被搶之後，警方可以會因此再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">增加休班狗嘅裝備</span></span>，例如手扣，胡椒噴霧，甚至係佩槍，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白色恐怖</span></span>猖狂至此，依家退一步已經會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">粉身碎骨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點都好，萬事小心，不要戀戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />軍裝到之前一定要散，Be Water<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del></del>"},{"pid":"6c990c00d18709710fcda1d3f7dcd2f54e23633b","tid":1561327,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7b388f5caa2367bf220b2dcad6fa972b916e76ba","tid":1561327,"uid":57868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"我地都係休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354ac369dd439b8106f7ab1dbdd3dc7cb723f348","tid":1561327,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"有帶警棍先好，容易identify<br />\n之前啲人話麻包袋定咩，咁樣唔會誤傷"},{"pid":"2c6682b5ab5b64ba45fa328151c72fefa3273a8b","tid":1561327,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"莫洛托夫的雞尾酒"},{"pid":"a5476d7e90aa90f26e4f5eb6415c871dabb00249","tid":1561327,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"唔見左碌棍都幾好笑"},{"pid":"7fb91a8d60b74e4eeee27e22232d606493e8f598","tid":1561327,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c86f6a/f/800x0/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190708/720pix/1562518426_416d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fc86f6a%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190708%2F720pix%2F1562518426_416d.jpg&h=a072ff57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9c43f5188365adfdafaffb6d00d9facef5458ab","tid":1561327,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"全世界都帶伸縮警棍"},{"pid":"38b90a7126442498d834c09ca1e2342b1bccab41","tid":1561327,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wq59qkT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWq59qkT.png&h=c4fb40f4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}